flowchart TD
    CSV[songs.csv] -->|load_songs| SL[Song List]
    UP[User Prefs\ngenre · mood · energy · likes_acoustic] --> LOOP

    SL --> LOOP[For each song in list]

    LOOP --> G{Genre match?}
    G -- yes --> GP[+2.0 pts]
    G -- no --> GP0[+0.0 pts]

    LOOP --> M{Mood match?}
    M -- yes --> MP[+1.0 pts]
    M -- no --> MP0[+0.0 pts]

    LOOP --> E[Energy similarity]
    E --> EP[+0.0 to 1.0 pts]

    LOOP --> A{Acoustic fit?}
    A -- yes --> AP[+0.5 pts]
    A -- no --> AP0[+0.0 pts]

    GP & GP0 & MP & MP0 & EP & AP & AP0 --> SUM[Sum all points]
    SUM --> EXP[Build explanation string]
    EXP --> COLLECT[Collect: song, score, explanation]

    COLLECT --> NEXT{More songs?}
    NEXT -- yes --> LOOP
    NEXT -- no --> SORT[Sort by score DESC]
    SORT --> TOPK[Slice top K]
    TOPK --> OUT[Print recommendations]
